No interactions (P > 0.10) between duration of feeding (continuous or not) or form (powder vs. granular) of SDP were noted (Table 3
). Compared with that of control broilers, the addition of SDP improved (P < 0.05) average daily gain (ADG), average daily feed intake (ADFI), and feed efficiency (gain:feed) at each period (d 0 to 14 and 0 to 35; Table 3). Likewise, compared with control broilers on d 35, SDP improved (P < 0.05) BW (Table 4
) and liveability (Table 4; Figure 1
).
